data.description: Welcome to LEILANI HEIGHTS! The most sought neighborhood in Jensen Beach. 3/2/1 CBS pool home plus a brand new 10X12 Tuffs shed (hurricane rated )! Plenty of room to park all your toys- BOAT, RV or a trailer. LOW HOA fees of $10 a month, just to give you that neighborhood feel, but let you enjoy your home your way! NEW IMPACT WINDOWS throughout (Miami Dade rated) , brand NEW METAL ROOF, wood like porcelain tile throughout, updated kitchen with quartz countertops, SS appliances! Closed in PATIO plus outside lanai opens up to a BRAND NEW SALT WATER POOL! Extended driveway and new white PVC fence! Walking distance to A rated schools! Near downtown Stuart and Jensen Beach and Treasure Coast Beaches! Over 150K worth of UPGRADES! This house a true GEM! Buyer can assume current loan at 3.6%!
